WEBVTT

00:14:57.465 --> 00:15:00.375
AG: Yeah, I know you're really
feeling sorry for these guys.

00:15:01.018 --> 00:15:04.037
But remember, the mantra
is a "fit for every man,"

00:15:04.061 --> 00:15:05.242
and at many companies,

00:15:05.266 --> 00:15:08.842
this issue might never reach someone
in a position to do something about it.

00:15:08.866 --> 00:15:11.716
But at Bonobos,
before a new collection is released,

00:15:11.740 --> 00:15:15.380
they hold a special meeting to collect
input from employees in every role.

00:15:15.404 --> 00:15:19.625
BA: Merchandising, planning, design,
production, marketing, tech --

00:15:19.649 --> 00:15:22.702
AG: And most importantly,
employees like Tyler Kantor,

00:15:22.726 --> 00:15:24.718
who interact with customers one-on-one.

00:15:24.742 --> 00:15:28.882
TK: I remember my regional
manager at the time actually nudging me,

00:15:28.906 --> 00:15:30.445
like, "Hey, Tyler, speak up.